CRM System Management Presentation Documentation

1. Project Overview
- Smart CRM System ek complete solution hai for sales lead management, user management, reporting, and business analytics.
- Backend FastAPI (Python) par based hai, frontend HTML/CSS/JS templates use karta hai.

2. System Architecture
- Modular structure: Python scripts (main logic), templates (UI), static files (CSS/JS), tools (utility scripts), uploads (user/report files).
- Database: MySQL for data storage (leads, users, targets, audit logs, reports).
- REST API endpoints for all major features.

3. Key Features
- User Authentication & Role Management
- Lead Management (Add, Edit, Delete, View)
- Target Management (Set, Track, Calculate Progress)
- Dashboard (Stats, Widgets, Recent Activities)
- Permission Management (Admin/User roles)
- Audit Logging (User actions, security)
- Report Management (Upload, Download, View)
- Security Audit (API & UI)

4. Functional Flows
A. Login Flow
   - User enters credentials → Validation → Session create → Dashboard redirect
B. Lead Management
   - Add/Edit/Delete/View lead → Form validation → DB update → Audit log
C. Target Management
   - Set target → Assign users → Track progress → Calculate completion
D. Dashboard
   - Show stats, charts, widgets → Permission-based data visibility
E. Report Management
   - Upload PDF report → Validate file → Save to DB & uploads folder → Download/View
F. Permission & Audit
   - Assign/revoke permissions → Log user actions → Security audit table

5. Form Fields & Validation
- All forms have required fields, type checks, length checks, custom validation (email, phone, etc.)
- Error messages for invalid input

6. Error Handling
- API error codes (400, 401, 403, 500)
- User-friendly error messages
- Database/file upload errors handled gracefully

7. Security & Compliance
- Role-based access control
- Audit logs for all sensitive actions
- Secure file uploads
- CORS enabled for safe API access

8. Reporting & Analytics
- Lead status percentage calculation
- Target progress calculation
- Export options (PDF, Excel)
- Dashboard analytics

9. Deployment & Maintenance
- Easy deployment (Python, FastAPI, Uvicorn)
- Modular code for easy updates
- Database backup & restore
- Static files for UI customization

10. Screens & UI Behavior
- Login: Form, error, redirect
- Dashboard: Stats, widgets, actions
- Leads: List, add, edit, delete
- Users: List, add, edit, permissions
- Targets: Set, track, calculate
- Reports: Upload, download, view
- Settings: Configure, save, validate
- Audit/Security: Logs, table, actions

11. Future Enhancements
- Mobile app integration
- Advanced analytics (AI/ML)
- Third-party integrations (email, calendar)
- Customizable workflows

12. Summary
- Smart CRM System ek scalable, secure, aur feature-rich solution hai for sales lead management.
- Sabhi business, security, aur reporting needs ko address karta hai.

